reviews.text:
Good local lunch place with a daily menu and lunch set. No service charge and prices and quality is good.
One more point that is very positive: All staff are very friendly(!), I have never seen an unfriendly staff in this local restaurant.
Tasty food. The food choices never gets old with their rotating menu
Great food at an affordable price

Good for a quick bite.  Quality of food generally good here but more importantly,  one can sense the pride and thoughtfulness of the owners/operators in their preparations. And this extends to the service as well as the general attitude of the staff. Says a lot since this cafe/canteen is a typical one that serves lunch crowd in Hk.
The lunch is okay. I suggest you arrive by 12:25pm or you have to wait for a while to get a seat.
